msgstr "<variable id=\"align\"><link href=\"text/smath/guide/align.xhp\">ການຈັດວາງແຖວສ່ວນປະກອບຂອງສູດດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ</link></variable>"

#. eUZmq
#: align.xhp
msgctxt ""
"align.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154657\n"
"help.text"
msgid "How do you align characters in $[officename] Math quickly and easily?"
msgstr "ທ່ານຈະຈັດວາງແຖວຕົວອັກສອນໃນ $[officename] Math ໃຫ້ໄວ ແລະ ງ່າຍດາຍໄດ້ແນວໃດ?"

#. EJ2GY
#: align.xhp
msgctxt ""
"align.xhp\n"
"par_id3150249\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To accomplish this, you must define empty groups and character strings. They do not require any space, but carry information that helps in the alignment process."
msgstr "ເພື່ອເຮັດສິ່ງນີ້, ທ່ານຕ້ອງກຳນົດກຸ່ມວ່າງ ແລະ ຊຸດຕົວອັກສອນ. ພວກມັນບໍ່ຕ້ອງການບ່ອນວ່າງໃດໆ, ແຕ່ຈະບັນຈຸຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຊ່ວຍໃນຂະບວນການຈັດວາງແຖວ."

#. BLcvk
#: align.xhp
msgctxt ""
"align.xhp\n"
"par_id3153912\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To create empty groups, enter curly brackets <emph>{}</emph> in the Commands window. In the following example, the goal is to achieve a line break so that the plus signs are beneath one another, even though one less character is entered in the upper line:"
msgstr "ເພື່ອສ້າງກຸ່ມວ່າງ, ໃຫ້ປ້ອນວົງເລັບປີກກາ <emph>{}</emph> ໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມຄຳສັ່ງ. ໃນຕົວຢ່າງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້, ຈຸດປະສົງແມ່ນເພື່ອຂຶ້ນແຖວໃໝ່ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ເຄື່ອງໝາຍບວກຢູ່ຊື່ກັນ, ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າຈະມີຕົວອັກສອນໜ້ອຍກວ່າໃນແຖວເທິງກໍຕາມ:"

#. wDfhJ
#: align.xhp
msgctxt ""
"align.xhp\n"
"par_id3143229\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Empty character strings are a simple way to ensure that texts and formulas are left-aligned. They are defined using double inverted commas \"\" . Make sure you do not use any typographic inverted commas. Example:"
msgstr "ຊຸດຕົວອັກສອນວ່າງແມ່ນວິທີທີ່ງ່າຍເພື່ອໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າຂໍ້ຄວາມ ແລະ ສູດຖືກຈັດວາງຊ້າຍ. ພວກມັນຖືກກຳນົດໂດຍໃຊ້ເຄື່ອງໝາຍຄຳເວົ້າຄູ່ \"\" . ໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າທ່ານບໍ່ໄດ້ໃຊ້ເຄື່ອງໝາຍຄຳເວົ້າແບບ typographic. ຕົວຢ່າງ:"

#. C6Ky9
#: align.xhp
msgctxt ""
"align.xhp\n"
"par_id3153809\n"
"help.text"
msgid "\"A further example.\" newline a+b newline \"\"c-d"
msgstr "\"ຕົວຢ່າງເພີ່ມເຕີມ.\" newline a+b newline \"\"c-d"

