#. k9ADA
#: attributes.xhp
msgctxt ""
"attributes.xhp\n"
"par_id3148870\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Some parts of formulas are always formatted bold or italic by default."
msgstr "ບາງສ່ວນຂອງສູດຈະຖືກຈັດຮູບແບບເປັນຕົວໜາ ຫຼື ຕົວເນີ້ງສະເໝີໂດຍຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ."

#. 7A7Vi
#: attributes.xhp
msgctxt ""
"attributes.xhp\n"
"par_id3150210\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can remove these attributes using \"nbold\" and \"nitalic\". Example:"
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດເອົາຄຸນລັກສະນະເຫຼົ່ານີ້ອອກໄດ້ໂດຍໃຊ້ \"nbold\" ແລະ \"nitalic\". ຕົວຢ່າງ:"

#. MCJxc
#: attributes.xhp
msgctxt ""
"attributes.xhp\n"
"par_id3149872\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the second formula, the a is not italic. The b is bold. You cannot change the plus sign by this method."
msgstr "ໃນສູດທີສອງ, ຕົວ a ບໍ່ແມ່ນຕົວເນີ້ງ. ຕົວ b ແມ່ນຕົວໜາ. ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດປ່ຽນເຄື່ອງໝາຍບວກດ້ວຍວິທີນີ້ໄດ້."

