#. z6zop
#: brackets.xhp
msgctxt ""
"brackets.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154511\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Inserting fractions into formulas"
msgstr "ການແຊກເລກເສດສ່ວນລົງໃນສູດ"

#. jPtfJ
#: brackets.xhp
msgctxt ""
"brackets.xhp\n"
"par_id3146971\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the case of a fraction whose numerator and denominator consist of a product, a sum, and so on, the values that belong together must be bracketed together."
msgstr "ໃນກໍລະນີຂອງເລກເສດສ່ວນທີ່ຕົວເສດ ແລະ ຕົວສ່ວນປະກອບດ້ວຍຜົນຄູນ, ຜົນບວກ, ແລະ ອື່ນໆ, ຄ່າທີ່ຢູ່ຮ່ວມກັນຕ້ອງຖືກໃສ່ວົງເລັບໄວ້ນຳກັນ."

#. 4bWFt
