#. hYDBe
#: newline.xhp
msgctxt ""
"newline.xhp\n"
"par_id3154702\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Create a line break by using the \"newline\" command. Everything coming after the line break is placed on the next line."
msgstr "ສ້າງການຂຶ້ນແຖວໃໝ່ໂດຍໃຊ້ຄຳສັ່ງ \"newline\". ທຸກຢ່າງທີ່ຕາມຫຼັງການຂຶ້ນແຖວໃໝ່ຈະຖືກວາງໄວ້ໃນແຖວຖັດໄປ."

