#. FGjG4
#: text.xhp
msgctxt ""
"text.xhp\n"
"hd_id8509170\n"
"help.text"
msgid "How to enter direct text strings that do not get interpreted?"
msgstr "ວິທີການປ້ອນຊຸດຂໍ້ຄວາມໂດຍກົງທີ່ບໍ່ຖືກຕີຄວາມໝາຍ?"

#. 8AWkB
#: text.xhp
msgctxt ""
"text.xhp\n"
"par_id337229\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Some text strings get interpreted as operators automatically. Sometimes this is not what you want. If you want to write W<emph>*</emph> (a letter with a superscripted asterisk), the asterisk will be interpreted as a multiplication operator. Enclose the direct text within double quotes or add spaceholders."
msgstr "ບາງຊຸດຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະຖືກຕີຄວາມໝາຍວ່າເປັນຕົວດຳເນີນການໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ. ບາງຄັ້ງນີ້ບໍ່ແມ່ນສິ່ງທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການ. ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການຂຽນ W<emph>*</emph> (ຕົວອັກສອນທີ່ມີດອກຈັນຢູ່ເທິງ), ດອກຈັນຈະຖືກຕີຄວາມໝາຍວ່າເປັນຕົວດຳເນີນການຄູນ. ໃຫ້ໃສ່ຂໍ້ຄວາມໂດຍກົງໄວ້ໃນເຄື່ອງໝາຍຄຳເວົ້າຄູ່ ຫຼື ເພີ່ມຕົວວາງຕຳແໜ່ງ."

#. HCpMB
#: text.xhp
msgctxt ""
"text.xhp\n"
"par_idN105D0\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Examples:"
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງ:"

#. aKbTy
#: text.xhp
msgctxt ""
"text.xhp\n"
"par_id521866\n"
"help.text"
msgid "An imported MathType formula contains the following string"
msgstr "ສູດ MathType ທີ່ນຳເຂົ້າປະກອບດ້ວຍຂໍ້ຄວາມຕໍ່ໄປນີ້"

#. pgDrE
#: text.xhp
msgctxt ""
"text.xhp\n"
"par_id755943\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you have set up Math to convert imported MathType formulas (in <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</caseinline><defaultinline>Tools - Options</defaultinline></switchinline> - Load/Save - Microsoft Office), you see the formula with a placeholder instead of the asterisk."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານໄດ້ຕັ້ງຄ່າ Math ເພື່ອແປງສູດ MathType ທີ່ນຳເຂົ້າ (ໃນ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">%PRODUCTNAME - ຄ່າກຳນົດ</caseinline><defaultinline>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</defaultinline></switchinline> - ໂຫຼດ/ບັນທຶກ - Microsoft Office), ທ່ານຈະເຫັນສູດທີ່ມີຕົວວາງຕຳແໜ່ງແທນເຄື່ອງໝາຍດອກຈັນ."

#. VXaga
#: text.xhp
msgctxt ""
"text.xhp\n"
"par_id5988952\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Change {*} to {} * {} as in the following formula:"
msgstr "ປ່ຽນ {*} ເປັນ {} * {} ຄືໃນສູດຕໍ່ໄປນີ້:"

#. HGq8j
#: text.xhp
msgctxt ""
"text.xhp\n"
"par_id4941557\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can also use W^\"*\" to enter the character as direct text."
msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດໃຊ້ W^\"*\" ເພື່ອປ້ອນຕົວອັກສອນເປັນຂໍ້ຄວາມໂດຍກົງ."

#. qELLZ
#: text.xhp
msgctxt ""
"text.xhp\n"
"par_id9961851\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Some formulas start with an = sign. Use \"=\" to enter that character as direct text."
msgstr "ບາງສູດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍເຄື່ອງໝາຍ =. ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ \"=\" ເພື່ອປ້ອນຕົວອັກສອນນັ້ນເປັນຂໍ້ຄວາມໂດຍກົງ."
